<title>UK: BAA June cargo traffic up 8.5 pct.</title>
<headline>BAA June cargo traffic up 8.5 pct.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-07-10</dateline>
<text>
<p>Cargo handled at BAA's seven UK airports rose 8.5 percent in June from a year ago to 136,279 tonnes.</p>
<p>Traffic at Heathrow dominated the statistics rising 10.9 percent to just over 100,000 tonnes whilst Gatwick's lead over Standsted continued to narrow compared to year ago data now BA increasingly uses Stansted for cargo.</p>
